@startuml
hide empty description

[*] --> Scheduled : Plant Added / Cycle Calculated

Scheduled --> Notified : System time matches scheduled time
Scheduled --> Queued : Time matches "Do Not Disturb" hours
Queued --> Notified : Quiet hours end

state Notified {
  [*] --> PendingResponse
}

Notified --> Watered : User selects "Mark as Watered"
Notified --> Snoozed : User selects "Snooze"
Notified --> Forwarded : User selects "Nag Someone Else"
Notified --> Faulty : User selects "Mark Faulty Reminder"

PendingResponse --> Overdue : 24 hours pass without interaction
Overdue --> Watered : User interacts & marks watered
Overdue --> Snoozed : User interacts & snoozes

Snoozed --> Notified : Snooze duration expires
Forwarded --> Notified : Forwarded user receives notification

Watered --> Scheduled : System calculates next watering date
Faulty --> [*] : Awaits user/support intervention

@enduml
